
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-nikander-esp-beet-mode-09.txt'>
    <title>"A Bound End-to-End Tunnel (BEET) mode for ESP", Pekka Nikander, Jan Melen</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-nikander-esp-beet-mode-09.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies a new mode, called Bound End-to-End Tunnel (BEET) mode, for IPsec ESP.  The new mode augments the existing ESP tunnel and transport modes.  For end-to-end tunnels, the new mode provides limited tunnel mode semantics without the regular tunnel mode overhead.  The mode is intended to support new uses of ESP, including mobility and multi-address multi-homing.</description>
    <dc:date>2008-08-04T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
